The '''Lekeythang Football Field''' is a football field located in the municipality of [[Punakha]] in [[Bhutan]]. Its maximum seating capacity is 1000 people and is the home pitch of [[Ugyen Academy F.C.]].<ref>https://int.soccerway.com/venues/bhutan/lekeythang-football-field/v17283/</ref>

